This really stinks, you know?

01:47:29.860 --> 01:47:32.860
Why'd you have to take me to see Dr. McBride anyway?

01:47:32.860 --> 01:47:34.860
Oh, I don't know.

01:47:34.860 --> 01:47:36.860
Maybe going into shock at the nurse's station

01:47:36.860 --> 01:47:38.860
and raving about seeing your dead best friend

01:47:38.860 --> 01:47:40.860
