01:47:40.860 --> 01:47:42.860
You know, I've never missed the first day of fishing season?

01:47:42.860 --> 01:47:43.860
Not once.

01:47:43.860 --> 01:47:45.860
Not even here, Ricky.

01:47:45.860 --> 01:47:47.860
You died.

01:47:47.860 --> 01:47:49.860
Mike, I'm sorry.

01:47:49.860 --> 01:47:51.860
The doctor said bed rest, and that's exactly what it's going to be.

01:47:51.860 --> 01:47:53.860
You don't think I'm crazy, don't you?

01:47:53.860 --> 01:47:55.860
We just don't want you to know I saw what I saw.

01:47:55.860 --> 01:47:57.860
I know you think you did.

01:47:57.860 --> 01:47:59.860
But I also believe the doctor,

01:47:59.860 --> 01:48:01.860
when he says that you should be in bed.

01:48:01.860 --> 01:48:03.860
Stop the car.

01:48:03.860 --> 01:48:08.260
I just saw Ricky riding his bike down Hanover Road.

01:48:08.260 --> 01:48:11.260
Dad, please, this will prove I'm not crazy.

01:48:11.260 --> 01:48:28.540
That's him.

01:48:28.540 --> 01:48:45.330
Sorry.

01:48:45.330 --> 01:48:48.330
That's it. It's bedtime for you, pal.

01:48:48.330 --> 01:48:52.330
Didn't-didn't you just think for just a second that was Ricky?

01:48:52.330 --> 01:48:57.560
No, son.

01:48:57.560 --> 01:48:59.560
You didn't?

01:48:59.560 --> 01:49:01.560
Mike, Ricky's dead.

01:49:01.560 --> 01:49:11.790
Let's go home.

01:49:11.790 --> 01:49:13.790
Please, enough with the thermometer.

01:49:13.790 --> 01:49:16.790
The pork has been poked and prodded enough for one day.

01:49:16.790 --> 01:49:18.790
The doctor says he just needs some rest.

01:49:18.790 --> 01:49:20.790
Uh-huh. I knew it.

01:49:20.790 --> 01:49:22.790
99.6.

01:49:22.790 --> 01:49:24.790
Good. When he hits 100, we'll sell.

01:49:24.790 --> 01:49:26.790
I don't get it.

01:49:26.790 --> 01:49:28.790
It's a joke about stocks, Ben.

01:49:28.790 --> 01:49:30.790
I'm gonna go get a movie.

01:49:30.790 --> 01:49:32.790
Can we get you anything while we're out?

01:49:32.790 --> 01:49:34.790
Uh, no, I think we'll all write that. Thanks.

01:49:34.790 --> 01:49:36.790
Let's go, kiddo.

01:49:36.790 --> 01:49:38.790
Can I stay for a little while?

01:49:38.790 --> 01:49:40.790
Your brother needs his rest.

01:49:40.790 --> 01:49:42.790
It's okay, Mom. He's only gonna be here for a little while.

01:49:42.790 --> 01:49:44.790
Please?

01:49:44.790 --> 01:49:46.790
All right.

01:49:46.790 --> 01:49:48.790
But the minute Mike starts nodding off, you hit the road.

01:49:48.790 --> 01:49:55.080
Thanks.

01:49:55.080 --> 01:49:57.080
I'm really gonna miss you not going fishing tomorrow.

01:49:57.080 --> 01:49:59.080
I wish you can go.

01:49:59.080 --> 01:50:01.080
Yeah, me too.

01:50:01.080 --> 01:50:03.080
I've never been to the river without you.

01:50:03.080 --> 01:50:05.080
Hey, no sweat.

01:50:05.080 --> 01:50:07.080
I was going there when I was 10.

01:50:07.080 --> 01:50:09.080
Besides, you'll have your friends with you. That'd be cool.

01:50:09.080 --> 01:50:11.080
Just like you used to go with Ricky.

01:50:11.080 --> 01:50:17.020
Yeah.

01:50:17.020 --> 01:50:21.700
Did you really see him?

01:50:21.700 --> 01:50:23.700
I swear I did, Ben.

01:50:23.700 --> 01:50:25.700
Everyone thinks I'm a few sandwiches short of a picnic.

01:50:25.700 --> 01:50:27.700
I believe you.

01:50:27.700 --> 01:50:29.700
Thanks.

01:50:29.700 --> 01:50:34.170
If everyone did, I wouldn't be stuck in bed all stinkin' weekend.

01:50:34.170 --> 01:50:36.170
Mom and Dad are going grocery shopping on Saturdays, right?

01:50:36.170 --> 01:50:38.170
Before they leave, come up and wake me.

01:50:38.170 --> 01:50:40.170
I'll go with you.

01:50:40.170 --> 01:50:42.170
You will?

01:50:42.170 --> 01:50:44.170
It's not like I'm really sick anyway, right?

01:50:44.170 --> 01:50:47.640
Cool. So what did Dad's joke before me?

01:50:47.640 --> 01:50:49.640
Was it dirty?

01:50:49.640 --> 01:50:51.640
No, it was just too grown up for you to understand, Ben.

01:50:51.640 --> 01:50:53.640
Besides, it wasn't that funny.

01:50:53.640 --> 01:50:55.640
I think yours are much better.

01:50:55.640 --> 01:50:57.640
Want to hear one?

01:50:57.640 --> 01:50:59.640
Hit me, brother.

01:50:59.640 --> 01:51:01.640
Okay. Ask me why I'm a great comedian.

01:51:01.640 --> 01:51:03.640
Why are you a great comedian?

01:51:03.640 --> 01:51:05.640
It's...

01:51:05.640 --> 01:52:05.500
Hey!

01:52:05.500 --> 01:52:07.500
What do you think you're going?

01:52:07.500 --> 01:52:09.500
Well...

01:52:09.500 --> 01:52:11.500
Well...

01:52:11.500 --> 01:52:13.500
I need my taco box.

01:52:13.500 --> 01:52:15.500
Yeah. Yeah, my taco box.

01:52:15.500 --> 01:52:17.500
You know what's in the garage?

01:52:17.500 --> 01:52:19.500
Has everyone here gone wacky?

01:52:19.500 --> 01:52:21.500
Come on, go get your stuff.

01:52:21.500 --> 01:52:23.500
Mom and I will give you a ride to Gower's River.

01:52:23.500 --> 01:52:25.500
That's all right, Dad. I'll walk.

01:52:25.500 --> 01:52:27.500
Don't be ridiculous. It's a long hike.

01:52:27.500 --> 01:52:29.500
Okay.

01:52:29.500 --> 01:52:31.500
Good.

01:52:31.500 --> 01:53:17.050
I don't sound so excited about it.

01:53:17.050 --> 01:54:31.910
Stop it, Ben.

01:54:31.910 --> 01:54:33.910
Fran got killed?

01:54:33.910 --> 01:54:46.340
Keep moving. I don't want to hear any more about Ricky.

01:54:46.340 --> 01:54:50.620
Ricky? Ricky!

01:54:50.620 --> 01:54:59.460
Ricky!

01:54:59.460 --> 01:55:03.740
Ricky!

01:55:03.740 --> 01:55:11.340
Here I am, Mike.

01:55:11.340 --> 01:55:13.340
Here I am?

01:55:13.340 --> 01:55:15.340
Just like that?

01:55:15.340 --> 01:55:29.430
Here I am.

01:55:29.430 --> 01:55:31.430
What do you want from me?

01:55:31.430 --> 01:55:38.360
Sorry, it was an accident.

01:55:38.360 --> 01:55:40.360
Sorry, another accident.

01:55:40.360 --> 01:55:56.220
Ricky...

01:55:56.220 --> 01:55:58.220
I tried to save you, all right?

01:55:58.220 --> 01:56:00.220
I tried. I did whatever I could.

01:56:00.220 --> 01:56:02.220
If that wasn't good enough, do whatever you want to me.

01:56:02.220 --> 01:56:04.220
Am I here to hurt you, Mike?

01:56:04.220 --> 01:56:06.220
You're my best friend.

01:56:06.220 --> 01:56:08.220
You try to save my life.

01:56:08.220 --> 01:56:10.220
Why do you keep coming after me?

01:56:10.220 --> 01:56:12.220
I'm here to warn you.

01:56:12.220 --> 01:56:14.220
Warn me?

01:56:14.220 --> 01:56:16.220
That's great. Warn me.

01:56:16.220 --> 01:56:18.220
You know...

01:56:18.220 --> 01:56:20.220
What's so important that you have to come up here and...

01:56:20.220 --> 01:56:22.220
What?

01:56:22.220 --> 01:56:36.220
Danger, Mike.

01:56:36.220 --> 01:56:38.220
I tried to tell you yesterday at school.

01:56:38.220 --> 01:56:40.220
You must go to him before it's too late.

01:56:40.220 --> 01:56:42.220
He's at the bridge.

01:56:42.220 --> 01:57:07.540
My bridge.

01:57:07.540 --> 01:57:09.540
I miss you, Ricky.

01:57:09.540 --> 01:57:11.540
I miss you too, Mike.

01:57:11.540 --> 01:57:13.540
Get going.

01:57:13.540 --> 01:57:15.540
It's a long ride and we don't want to

01:57:15.540 --> 01:59:40.870
